oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Original wills, Achtzehner, Maria Magdalena, 1881 January 26
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An original will of Maria Magdalena Achtzehner, dated January 26th, 1881. Illustrates the first page of the document. The envelope notation reads “Maria Magdalena Achtzehner Will, ‘English,’ Book ‘V’ page 410.” 1 page is in German. Forms part of Record Group 16, Original Wills, 1780-1925.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Achtzehner family
